data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, end unit townhome. As you approach this home, you'll notice its fresh exterior paint, fenced in backyard and extra parking.  Step inside to discover the inviting living room, complete with a cozy fireplace. The main floor features updated flooring, a laundry room with updated 1/2 bathroom, and the dining area has a sliding glass door that leads out to the fully fenced yard.  Upstairs you will find three bedrooms. The newly updated bathroom on this level adds a touch of luxury. Don't miss your chance to call it home sweet home!
